---
title: Claude Tool-Use Protocol
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant C as 🧠 Claude
    participant T as 🔧 Tool (Your Code)

    U->>C: "What is 1847 * 293 + 17?"
    Note over C: REASON: I need the calculator
    C->>U: tool_use(calculator, "1847 * 293 + 17")
    Note over U: stop_reason = "tool_use"
    U->>T: Execute calculator("1847 * 293 + 17")
    T->>U: "541388"
    U->>C: tool_result(id, "541388")
    Note over C: OBSERVE: Result is 541,388
    C->>U: "1847 × 293 + 17 = 541,388"
    Note over U: stop_reason = "end_turn"
